        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="italic">Recalling</span> its resolutions <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/60/254">60/254</a> of 8 May 2006, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/62/247">62/247</a> of 3 April 2008, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/63/250">63/250</a> of 24 December 2008, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/66/234">66/234</a> of 24 December 2011, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/67/255">67/255</a> of 12 April 2013, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/68/252">68/252</a> of 27 December 2013, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/71/263">71/263</a> of 23 December 2016, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/77/278">77/278</a> of 18 April 2023 and <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/78/246">78/246</a> of 22 December 2023,</p>
